WEBVTT

00:04.932 --> 00:08.982
This incredible, colorful city will only last a few months,...

00:10.762 --> 00:14.263
...but for one local designer, the seasonal spectacular is worth it.

00:19.428 --> 00:24.154
Jinnan Zheng is an award-winning ice sculptor and art teacher in Harbin, China.

00:25.315 --> 00:30.099
Harbin is known as the City of Ice, and each year hosts the incredible spectacle,...

00:30.397 --> 00:32.367
...the Harbin Snow and Ice Festival.

00:33.159 --> 00:35.652
These large-scale designs are remarkable.

